-- Saudi Arabia May Spend $80 Billion on Desalination, Awsat Says
-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 2012-03-18T07:06:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-18/saudi-arabia-may-spend-80-billion-on-desalination-awsat-says.html
Saudi Arabia plans to spend 300
billion riyals ($80 billion) on desalinated water projects over
20 years,  al-Sharq al-Awsat  reported, citing Abdul Rahman Al-
Ibrahim, governor of  Saline Water Conversion Corp.   To contact the reporter on this story:
